column2: Unlawful Entry: A subject who hadbeen previously arrested forviolating a barring notice wasobserved in the building.
Theft: A student reported the theftof a laptop that was left unattended
Theft: A student reported the theftof a phone that was left with a coatin a common unsecured area.
Credit Card Fraud: A studentreported fraudlet charges on acredit card
Drug Violation: A student wasfound in possession of drugs
Theft/Credit Card Fraud: A studentreported  the theft of a laptop andwallet containing credit cards. Thecredit cards were used to makefraudulent charges
Theft: A student reportedelectronics items were stolen froma backpack that was leftunattended.
Theft: A student reported the theftof a secured bike  from a bike rack
Theft: A student reported the theftof a secured bike from a bike rack.
Alcohol Violation: An underagedstudent was found in possession ofalcohol.
